{"tid":2498570,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史新高, 新都城頂樓1163萬，644呎，呎價18,059","createTime":"2021-04-21T09:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T14:51:09.000Z","uid":73269,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fa3924c906c526ed4d4c2b841dc2e885d3025152","tid":2498570,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"歷史新高價<br />\n市場續現高價，將軍澳新都城套3房連天台1163萬元，為過去1年新高價。美聯物業新都城分行區域經理黃少明指出，新都城2期5座高層連天台，單位實用積644平方呎，另天台461呎，單位於去年10月以1,188萬元放盤，現以1,163萬元放盤，減價25萬元，實用呎價18,059元。原業主於2000年4月以323.3萬元購入，持貨21年帳面獲利839.8萬元。"},{"pid":"0369909761c7952c7eff660d793ed2d75a18d3dd","tid":2498570,"uid":387452,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"平到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f9536ee8784f5ee2e0d430a7b6326cf0e4009e","tid":2498570,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0369909761c7952c7eff660d793ed2d75a18d3dd","tid":2498570,"uid":387452,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"平到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:40:21.000Z","msg":"買樓易"},{"pid":"5a5d197cc8d4bb0c8304dcfd1008f6e83c997f31","tid":2498570,"uid":36138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"分層都19k, 連天台18k 係咩玩法？"},{"pid":"36f4af5b865742d0dfdc9e9a141588e7bcc67dea","tid":2498570,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5d197cc8d4bb0c8304dcfd1008f6e83c997f31","tid":2498570,"uid":36138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"分層都19k, 連天台18k 係咩玩法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"天台有D人怕漏水"},{"pid":"0ff1a635c05b1cb70d6a059b70c19ba4e4fefd48","tid":2498570,"uid":41484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:17:33.000Z","msg":"都唔係屋內直達天台，買返黎又要煩漏水"},{"pid":"122d51eb0264e1c39c